<emphasis id="1FC9EAB7C07E4B1CFF014B38FEE43290" bold="true" box="[192,339,1645,1671]" pageId="31" pageNumber="30">Distribution</emphasis>
(for map see 
<figureCitation id="B5862A20C07E4B1CFE2B4B38FD803290" box="[490,567,1645,1671]" captionStart="Figure 71" captionStartId="56.[194,270,1867,1893]" captionTargetBox="[192,1440,213,1828]" captionTargetId="figure-11@56.[192,1440,213,1828]" captionTargetPageId="56" captionText="Figure 71. Distribution map for Axina species: A. luzia, A. munda, A. minas, A. pallidioccabus, A. picta, A. pollex, A. polycaula, A. proxima, A. rio, A. villa, A. vista, A. nigrifrons, A. ochra." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4565003" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4565003/files/figure.png" pageId="31" pageNumber="30">Fig. 71</figureCitation>
). This species is known from 
<collectingCountry id="55AA7635C07E4B1CFC404B38FC723290" box="[897,965,1645,1671]" name="Brazil" pageId="31" pageNumber="30">Brazil</collectingCountry>
